P. Alpinus <foreign xml:lang="grc">σίλφιον</foreign> seu laserpitium e seminibus e<lb/>
Thracia delatis educasse in horto patavino sibi visus est:<lb/>
plantam delineatam habeo <hi rend="italic">Angelicae</hi> speciem dubiam.<ref target="#fn4">⁴</ref><lb/>
Eamdem credidit Bodaeus in horto coluisse; sed et de-<lb break="no"/>
scriptio et icon in <hi rend="italic">Angelican potius lucidam</hi> L., ameri-<lb break="no"/>
